# Scratch scripts — `_*.mjs` is the agreed convention for one-off / experimental
# scripts that are expected to be either promoted into a skill book / weapon
# action OR deleted. Keeping them out of source control prevents the
# accretion problem that bb8da53 cleaned up. If a script is genuinely
# reusable, drop the `_` prefix and commit it under `scripts/`.
scripts/_*.mjs

# Local scratch + diagnostic artifacts
tmp_inspect/
docs/screenshots/_scratch/
